  <p class=3DMsoNormal>Weapon Preference: Torpedoes and Ship Capturing</p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal>The eternal conflict between the Khemal and anti-Khe=
mal
  (Akhemal), is a cautionary tale of hubris and technological folly.<o:p></=
o:p></p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal>At a certain point in the Kehemal&#8217;s species de=
velopment,
  the ability to digitally transfer consciousness was discovered. Many Khem=
al
  jumped at the chance for strength and immortality in advanced machine bod=
ies,
  leaving their frail, short-lived biological bodies behind.<o:p></o:p></p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal>While both sides declare the other the aggressors, b=
oth
  the Khemal and Akhemal are absolutely dedicated to the eradication of the
  other&#8212;now, as a matter of vengeance and grievance, if not survival.=
 <o:p></o:p></p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal>The Khemal themselves are a short-lived species, lon=
g-lived
  individuals rarely reaching 40 standard years. They are known as passiona=
te
  artists and performers but also treat war and personal combat as a form of
  individual expression, to be practiced and honed.</p>
